      incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Eget nunc lobortis mattis aliquam
      faucibus purus. Maecenas volutpat blandit aliquam etiam erat velit scelerisque in
      dictum. Sit amet mauris commodo quis imperdiet massa tincidunt. Velit laoreet id
      donec ultrices tincidunt arcu non. Ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipiscing elit
      ut. Enim blandit volutpat maecenas volutpat blandit aliquam. Sollicitudin ac orci
      phasellus egestas tellus rutrum. Lectus proin nibh nisl condimentum id. Odio ut sem
      nulla pharetra. Nam at lectus urna duis convallis. Auctor elit sed vulputate mi sit
      amet. Viverra justo nec ultrices dui sapien eget mi proin sed. Risus quis varius
      quam quisque. Id nibh tortor id aliquet lectus proin nibh.
    </p>
    <div class='space-y-16'>
      <h2>Meet our leadership</h2>
      <div class='grid gap-28 py-20 md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-12'>
        <div class='group space-y-8 border-t-4 border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800'>
          <div class='mx-auto -mt-16 h-32 w-32 rotate-45 overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem]'>
            <Picture
              src={chairPortrait}
              formats={['avif', 'webp']}
              height={500}
              alt='chair-portrait'
              class='mx-auto h-full w-full -rotate-45 scale-125 object-cover transition duration-300 group-hover:scale-[1.4]'
